column2: SELECT   a.objID,   b.objID,            b.ra,            b.dec,            b.z,   b.zErr,   b.zConf,            b.petroMag_u,            b.petroMag_g,            b.petroMag_r,            b.petroMag_i,            b.petroMag_z,            b.petroMagErr_u,            b.petroMagErr_g,            b.petroMagErr_r,            b.petroMagErr_i,            b.petroMagErr_z,            b.extinction_u,            b.extinction_g,            b.extinction_r,            b.extinction_i,            b.extinction_z,            b.dered_u,            b.dered_g,            b.dered_r,            b.dered_i,            b.dered_z,            b.petroR5#_u,            b.petroR5#_g,            b.petroR5#_r,            b.petroR5#_i,            b.petroR5#_z,            b.petroR5#Err_u,            b.petroR5#Err_g,            b.petroR5#Err_r,            b.petroR5#Err_i,            b.petroR5#Err_z,            b.petroR9#_u,            b.petroR9#_g,            b.petroR9#_r,            b.petroR9#_i,            b.petroR9#_z,            b.petroR9#Err_u,            b.petroR9#Err_g,            b.petroR9#Err_r,            b.petroR9#Err_i,            b.petroR9#Err_z into mydb.MyTable from DR1#sample AS a   JOIN DR7sample AS b ON a.dr7ObjID  = b.objID      ORDER BY a.objID
